0Z","msg":"打贏大英帝國而立國<br />\n從當時最強帝國手上獨立<br />\n令大英帝國嘗試第一次海外戰爭失敗<br />\n<br />\n就如同聖經入面，大衛挑贏巨人哥利亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"立國之後不停擴張板圖，持續一百幾年<br />\n終於向西邊發展到三藩市個邊，即係西岸<br />\n<br />\n之後又打美西戰爭，拎埋關島，菲律賓<br />\n令勢力擴展至太平洋另一面<br />\n<br />\n打一戰（執雞）（由英國，歐洲來既美國人，重新插手歐洲）<br />\n<br />\n打二戰（執雞）（美國救返歐洲老牌國家，即係英法，打羸埋日本，以戰勝者身份號令全世界） 勢力由西歐至遠東日本，覆蓋半個地球）<br />\n<br />\n真係好傳奇<br />\n美國先係帝國殺手，德意志第三帝國（一半死係蘇聯手上），大日本帝國，大英帝國（二戰後取代英國）都係死係佢手上"},{"pid":"49e273f18a6c2d2ede017c94e56d9c73eeaf8f4d","tid":1025060,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cee657dc3a04d86a255483816f5ca2c0d007ad9","tid":1025060,"uid":18012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a6375e8292e861aee6f0b252cecc5e6fb415f36","tid":1025060,"uid":25055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"美國真係好勁<br />\n<br />\n立國歷史短 <br />\n<br />\n但聚集天下精英<br />\n<br />\n美帝國萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"打贏大英帝國而立國<br />\n從當時最強帝國手上獨立<br />\n令大英帝國嘗試第一次海外戰爭失敗<br />\n<br />\n就如同聖經入面，大衛挑贏巨人哥利亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"可以睇下 Washington's Crossing，講華盛頓係革命失利嗰陣奇襲英軍，重振士氣。仲有Thomas Paine 講美國點解要獨立 著作都好正。<br />\n&ldquo;Small islands not capable of protecting themselves, are the proper objects for kingdoms to take under their care; but there is something very absurd, in supposing a continent to be perpetually governed by an island. In no instance hath nature made the satellite larger than its primary planet, and as England and America, with respect to each other, reverses the common order of nature, it is evident they belong to different systems: England to Europe, America to itself.&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Washingtons-Crossing-Pivotal-Moments-American/dp/019518159X/ref=sr_1_1?k